CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 24, 1955, pg. A15 reads: "What's In It?...is the question Scott and Charles Harris III are wondering as they try to open an early Christmas gift.  The boys, 11 months and three years are the sone of Mr. and Mrs. Charles A. Harris II of Pittsburgh. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Scott Harris and Charles A. Harris Jr., sons of Charles A. "Little Teenie" Harris, seated on floor of bedroom, in Harris home at 7604 Mulford Street, Homewood
